						<summary>

						<p>Rock to the south of the Ōṭiguṇṭa tank.</p>						

						<p>This damaged record in late characters seems to refer to the construction of a tank and the grant of land to Tammarāya by Komarōbaḷi-nāyaka. Chidōja appears to have been the engraver of the record.</p>						

						<p>It is dated the cyclic year <hi rend="bold">Bhāva, Vaiśākha śu. 15,</hi> details are insufficient for verification.</p>						

						</summary>
